add_spell

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_spell -  This method adds a spell into the current spell list.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_spell(string name,
mixed ob,
mixed func)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the spell to add
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object the spell is on
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - the function to call for the spell
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/spells.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a spell into the current spell list.
.EP

